## President's Report

Bdale reported that some progress had been made on the previously
reported efforts to arrange discounts for SPI associated projects on
server and storage hardware from HP. The contract has been reviewed by
SPI's lawyer and board and we're now waiting for HP legal to review and
propose changes based on that feedback.

